        "sl_atr_mult": 1.0,
        "rationale": "Mean-reversion archetype with R:R 1.5 inside the [0.5, 2.0] mean-rev band; targets the snap-back to the 10-bar mean within the pooled h10 horizon rather than letting winners run, matching the forced-flow-exhaustion mechanism and the audit path's reachable geometry."
